<p>
	A wooden incense tower that is half the size of the bigger towers and is ideal for all types of cones or incense logs. The base has a good sized gold well for standing any size of incense cones. The lid then stands over this and has an intricate fretwork design to each side and in the top from which the smoke and aroma from your burning incense escapes.&nbsp;This tower is&nbsp;10.5cm tall.</p>
